                           <p>A <material key="marmor">white marble</material> funerary <objectType>stele</objectType>, cut in one piece, in the form of a pyramid surmounting a rectangular base (<width unit="metre">0.95</width> × <height unit="metre">0.50</height> × <depth unit="metre">0.50</depth>); all four sides of the pyramid and of the base are cut as panels within moulding. The top of the pyramid is broken away, but there are traces of a hole which would have held an insertion at the <term>apex</term>.</p>
                        </support>
