         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>The monument appears to be complete below; it must be assumed that it originally stood on another feature on which the last line of the epigram was inscribed.</p>
            <p>l. 9, <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΤΕΙΡΕΕΙ</foreign>, corrected by Cormack and Robert.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>He did not die, nor did he see the stream of Acheron, but in Olympus Asklepiodotos is among the stars—he who also built many splendid things for his motherland <gap unit="line" reason="lost" quantity="1"/>
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>See  <ref type="inscription" n="53" target="110068.xml"/>, and discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="V.8" target=".xml"/>.</p>
